<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>End-of-File on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/end-of-file/</link><description>Recent content in End-of-File on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/end-of-file/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] Go EOF Error Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/go/io-eof-2/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/go/io-eof-2/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="eof--end-of-file-fix"&gt;EOF — End of File Fix&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An EOF (End of File) error occurs when a read operation reaches the end of the data source. In Go, &lt;code&gt;io.EOF&lt;/code&gt; is returned by &lt;code&gt;Read()&lt;/code&gt; to indicate no more data is available.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="description"&gt;Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;io.EOF&lt;/code&gt; is not a true error — it&amp;rsquo;s a signal that the read operation completed successfully but there&amp;rsquo;s no more data. Many Go APIs return &lt;code&gt;io.EOF&lt;/code&gt; on the final &lt;code&gt;Read()&lt;/code&gt; call. Failing to handle &lt;code&gt;io.EOF&lt;/code&gt; properly causes programs to treat a normal end-of-data condition as an error.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] Go EOF Error Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/go/io-eof/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/go/io-eof/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="eof--end-of-file-fix"&gt;EOF — End of File Fix&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An EOF (End of File) error occurs when a read operation reaches the end of the data source. In Go, &lt;code&gt;io.EOF&lt;/code&gt; is returned by &lt;code&gt;Read()&lt;/code&gt; to indicate no more data is available.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="description"&gt;Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;io.EOF&lt;/code&gt; is not a true error — it&amp;rsquo;s a signal that the read operation completed successfully but there&amp;rsquo;s no more data. Many Go APIs return &lt;code&gt;io.EOF&lt;/code&gt; on the final &lt;code&gt;Read()&lt;/code&gt; call. Failing to handle &lt;code&gt;io.EOF&lt;/code&gt; properly causes programs to treat a normal end-of-data condition as an error.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>End of file</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cobol/end-of-file/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cobol/end-of-file/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An end of file (EOF) condition occurs when a READ statement attempts to read past the last record in a sequential file. This is indicated by FILE-STATUS 10 and the AT END clause.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reading past last record&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Missing AT END handling&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Empty file&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Incorrect loop termination&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-cobol" data-lang="cobol"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;PROCEDURE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;DIVISION&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; MAIN-PROCEDURE.&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;OPEN&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INPUT&lt;/span&gt; EMPLOYEE-FILE&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;PERFORM&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;UNTIL&lt;/span&gt; WS-FILE-STATUS &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;10&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;READ&lt;/span&gt; EMPLOYEE-FILE&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;AT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;END
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;MOVE &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;10&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;TO&lt;/span&gt; WS-FILE-STATUS&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;NOT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;AT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;END
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;DISPLAY&lt;/span&gt; EMPLOYEE-RECORD&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;END-READ
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;END-PERFORM
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;CLOSE&lt;/span&gt; EMPLOYEE-FILE&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-cobol" data-lang="cobol"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;PROCEDURE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;DIVISION&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; * Alternative: Use AT END flag
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;OPEN&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INPUT&lt;/span&gt; EMPLOYEE-FILE&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;MOVE &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;N&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;TO&lt;/span&gt; WS-EOF-FLAG&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;PERFORM&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;UNTIL&lt;/span&gt; WS-EOF-FLAG &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Y&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;READ&lt;/span&gt; EMPLOYEE-FILE&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;AT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;END
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;MOVE &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Y&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;TO&lt;/span&gt; WS-EOF-FLAG&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;NOT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;AT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;END
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; PROCESS-RECORD&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;END-READ
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;END-PERFORM
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-cobol" data-lang="cobol"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; * Example 1: Missing AT END
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;READ&lt;/span&gt; EMPLOYEE-FILE&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; * May get FILE-STATUS 10
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; * Example 2: Empty file
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;OPEN&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INPUT&lt;/span&gt; EMPLOYEE-FILE&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;READ&lt;/span&gt; EMPLOYEE-FILE&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;AT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;END&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;DISPLAY &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;File is empty&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;END-READ
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; Example &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;: Loop without EOF check&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;PERFORM&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;UNTIL&lt;/span&gt; FALSE
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;READ&lt;/span&gt; EMPLOYEE-FILE&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;DISPLAY&lt;/span&gt; WS-RECORD&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; * Infinite loop if no EOF handling
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cobol/file-status"&gt;File status error&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cobol/locked-record"&gt;Record locked&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>